     q:"Section C Answer any four  questions from this section.\nEach question carries 60 marks.\n\nLeaving Certificate Examination 2024  3\nBiology – Higher Level\nSections A and B and Answerbook Section A\nAnswer any five questions.\nWrite your answers in the spaces provided.",
